# pbizopoulos.github.io
https://pbizopoulos.github.io/

# Requirements
POSIX Shell & Utilities
Git
Docker

# Download
git clone https://github.com/pbizopoulos/pbizopoulos.github.io $HOME/github.com/pbizopoulos/pbizopoulos.github.io
cd $HOME/github.com/pbizopoulos/pbizopoulos.github.io/

# Development
cd docs/ && make clean check all && cd ..

# Staging
cd docs/ && make STAGING=1

